I kept an eye out for him and one day about a week later he pops up in my guild (Yup I am an OTWH member) and I thought well I'll be he is still around. I sent a tell to one of my officers to let them know that I have a BIG problem with this guy and explained why.  So after a few minutes the officer said I should get a tell from him and I did. He offered me 30p. I reminded him of the agreement and he said he would pay. So I was happy to think of being 1500p richer. I asked where to meet him and he said the bank and then went LD again.<br>
I finally got him to the bank a day or so later, after much and I mean MUCH prompting I managed to get all owed execpt 494p. Which I have been checking daily for his arse to show back up. <br>
Never the less he has not been on when I have. I will hound him for the rest, so if you see him send him a tell reminding him that he still owes me 494p. <br>
<br>
Safe and happy hunting to all. I am sorry to hear of your plight, believe me I feel for you. <br>
<br>
